<section xmlns:ns1="http://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/codified" xmlns:ns0="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <num>50-1731.03</num>
  <heading>Prohibition on distracted driving.</heading>
  <text>Distracted driving shall be prohibited. A person found guilty of distracted driving shall be subject to the fines and penalties set forth in § <cite path="§50-1731.06">50-1731.06</cite>(a).</text>
